'''Puma concolor''' (Linnaeus, 1771) ({{Vol-en|cougar, puma, or mountain lion}}; {{Vol-ru|пума}}; {{Vol-lv|puma, kalnu lauva, jeb pantera}}) — irā leļs [[Kaču saime|kaču saimis]] (''Felidae'') plieseigais [[zviers]]. ''Puma concolor'' dzeivoj Dīnavyd Amerikā i Pūstum Amerikis dīnavydā<ref name="ADV">[http://animaldiversity.ummz.umich.edu/site/accounts/information/Puma_concolor.html University of Michigan Museum of Zoology]</ref>.

